comment:
Interesting reading!
 As far as what you interpreted regarding Amber and her doing something regarding a child that was negative and reveals her character, Amber recently had a baby girl via surrogate in the midst of this legal trial.
From the timing and the way she seems to use the baby as a prop and for publicity photos, there is a lot of speculation that she strategically  had her daughter to help with her PR image and some how  try to use as an excuse to not serve jail time if she is convicted.
 What is even more devious and concerning is that during her affair with Elon  Musk  ( who she cheated on JD with 4 years ago) Amber and Elon created fertilized embryos together to have a child but had them stored. When the two broke up for good they were in a legal battle over the embryos; with Musk wanting them destroyed  and Amber wanting to use them to have a child ( and to secure millions of dollars in child alimony from Musk)
The public hasn't  been made aware of the final outcome of that legal case, but It seems that Amber was able to get access to an embryo and had it implanted in a surrogate for her.
She has not said who the father of her child is, but the heavy suspicion is on Elon Musk
( which puts him in hot water, because he was supposed to be In a happy relationship with Grimes and the two have a young child together.

Musk has been found to have been funding and helping AH with her  legal battle against JD and has been speculated to be cheating with Amber romantically yet again.
Even more recently  Musk and Grimes have officially broken up.

There is another rumor that his relationship with Grimes was more of a business arrangement  for positive press for him and increased celebrity status and more money for her. 
Elon and Grimes got pregnant right around the start of Musk and AH's embryo battle, so some people have speculated that  Musk coerced Grimes to have a baby with him to distance himself and deter Amber from trying to use the embryos  if she did happen to win the case. ( She would look like a gold digging homewrecker  if she did)

Grimes has stayed in interviews that she didn't even research or look into pregnancy and just jumped into it because of her love for Musk.
Elon is Very strategic and always tries  to control the narrative when it comes to his image in the media. 

It's  cold but to a multibillionaire like him, creating and then paying to raise a child would be no big deal 
( He barely has to spend time with his new son, other than for " Happy Family" photo posts on social media a few times a month and the child spends a lot of time with nannies)

IF true, these 3 celebrities are all pretty despicable  and I feel very sorry and concerned for their children :(

comment:
The pair divorced in 2016 and Johnny moved  on. When they were married Amber threatened that if he ever left her she would tell everyone he abused her, and that's exactly what she did.  She spent the next two years peddling her story to every media outlet she could find but her story never gained traction until the "me too" movement.    The final blow came with the Sun, a UK gossip rag, printed a lengthy article detailing her claims of abuse.  At that point her campaign was impacting his reputation and career and he had no choice but to fight back.  He released audio tapes and other information that clearly shows that she's the one who was abusive and manipulative and that she faked the bruises on her face with makeup.  However the judge ruled in favor of the magazine, so Johnny lost.

Now they're onto the next fight here in the US where he's suing her directly for defamation. Hopefully he'll win this one. Yes he too is publicly making allegations of abuse against her, but he has audio tapes of conversations to prove it, along with people who witnessed her behavior multiple times.  He really has no choice but to fight because it's his reputation and livelihood. He has lost his role in Pirates of the Caribbean and Fantastic Beasts. 

If she had just taken her 7 million settlement and moved on, none of this would be happening but she wanted to destroy him because he dared to break up with her.
